Privacy-Preserving Tensor Decomposition Over Encrypted Data in a Federated Cloud Environment 
Publisher: IEEE 
Cite This 
PDF 
Jun Feng ; Laurence T. Yang ; Qing Zhu ; Kim-Kwang Raymond Choo 
